b'Nico Young\xe2\x80\x99s talent is undeniable. In addition to being a model student and running his way to multiple wins on the track, he ranked #1 on DyeStat and was awarded this year\xe2\x80\x99s Gatorade National Boys Cross Country Runner of the Year. Now, we are excited to announce Nico is also the 2019-20 National Boys Track & Field #GatoradePOY. Winning this award makes him only the second athlete in the 35 year history of the program to win two Gatorade National titles in one year. Congrats Nico!'

b'At only 18 years old, Taylor Ewert is already an accomplished athlete: the only female runner in HS history to place in the top 10 at both NXN and Foot Locker in consecutive years in addition to being a national record-holder in seven distances. Now, Taylor can add one more accomplishment to her list: the 2019-20 National Girls Track & Field #GatoradePOY'
